<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Card Games</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <img id="dice" class="headerImg-1" src="/public/assets/image.png" alt="cards">
        <h1 class="title">Card Game API</h1>
        <img id="dice" class="headerImg-2" src="/public/assets/image.png" alt="cards">
    </header> 

    <main>            
        <div class="game-section">
            <h1 class="war-title">War</h1>
            <div class="thecard">
                <div class="card-inner">
                    <div class="thefront"></div>
                    <div class="theback">
                        <p>War is a simple card game for two players using a standard 52-card deck. Each player draws a card, and the higher card wins the round. If the cards are equal, a "war" occurs, where players reveal more cards to determine the winner. The game continues until one player has all the cards or they choose to stop.</p>
                        <a class="war-a" href="/war/start">Play War</a> 
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="game-section">
            <h1 class="bj-title">Blackjack</h1>
            <div class="thecard2">
                <div class="card-inner">
                    <div class="thefront2"></div>
                    <div class="theback2">
                        <p>Blackjack is a casino card game where players aim to get a hand value of 21 or closer without exceeding it. Players can "hit" for more cards or "stand" to keep their total, competing against the dealer.</p>
                        <a class="bj-a" href="/blackjack/start">Play Blackjack</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script type="module" src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.5.2/dist/ionicons/ionicons.esm.js"></script>
    <script nomodule src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.5.2/dist/ionicons/ionicons.js"></script>
</body>
</html>